sudo apt install default-jre picocom

--

MJPG STREAMER

sudo apt install libjpeg8-dev
cd mjpg_streamer inside hc3d project folder
cmake .
make install

- make sure libjpeg-dev is installed

--------- 3.
   
Serial testing:

picocom -b 115200 dev/relay --echo
stty --file=dev/relay --all
Symlinks: create folder hc3d/dev, add symlinks

Udev permissions:
nano /etc/udev/rules.d/66-tty.rules => KERNEL=="ttyUSB*",MODE="0666"

   
--------- 4.

Get fixed TTY devices:

- make symlinks to /home/pi/hc3d/dev/<path> from /dev/serial/by-path/<path>

--------- 

Get fixed webcam device:

- make symlink to  /dev/v4l/by-path/<path> in /home/pi/hc3d/dev/webca,